Matt enjoys reading and has a very large book collection. He also collects vinyl art toys
from sites like Kidrobot and My Plastic Heart. His varied interests lead him to start new
hobbies often, he likes to use a Daruma doll to set a goal for each one. Completed ones
are added to his eclectic collection of decor.
Matt is married and works full time as an app developer. He often works at coffee
shops or other public places for a change of scenery and the opportunity to
network. He enjoys travel and learning about other cultures.

Tressa’s hobbies include traveling, knitting, hiking and gardening. She loves artisan goods and
looks for unique items on Etsy. She collects things that have meaning to her, either from family
members or trinkets from her travels. She enjoys surrounding herself with things that bring her
joy and remind her of travels or other memories.
Tressa is a professional family and wedding photographer. She travels extensively
for her job, and has spent extended periods of time overseas. She has a brother
living in Tokyo and visits him regularly.
